modelQuery.sql: with Sales_target3 as (select ((SALES_TARGET.SALES_YEAR * 100) + SALES_TARGET.SALES_PERIOD) as Month_key, SALES_TARGET.SALES_YEAR as Sales_year, SALES_TARGET.SALES_PERIOD as Sales_period, SALES_TARGET.COUNTRY_CODE_RETAILER as Country_code_retailer, SALES_TARGET.SALES_STAFF_CODE as Sales_staff_code, SALES_TARGET.RETAILER_CODE as Retailer_code, SALES_TARGET.PRODUCT_TYPE_CODE as Product_type_code, SALES_TARGET.PRODUCT_BRAND_CODE as Product_brand_code, case when (SALES_TARGET.SALES_PERIOD in (1,3,5,7,8,10,12)) then ((((SALES_TARGET.SALES_YEAR * 100) + SALES_TARGET.SALES_PERIOD) * 100) + 31) when (SALES_TARGET.SALES_PERIOD in (4,6,9,11)) then ((((SALES_TARGET.SALES_YEAR * 100) + SALES_TARGET.SALES_PERIOD) * 100) + 30) else ((((SALES_TARGET.SALES_YEAR * 100) + SALES_TARGET.SALES_PERIOD) * 100) + 28) end as Day_key__sales_target_, SALES_TARGET.SALES_TARGET as Sales_target from [gosales].SALES_TARGET SALES_TARGET ) select Sales_target3.Month_key as Month_key, Sales_target3.Sales_year as Sales_year, Sales_target3.Sales_period as Sales_period, Sales_target3.Country_code_retailer as Country_code_retailer, Sales_target3.Sales_staff_code as Sales_staff_code, Sales_target3.Retailer_code as Retailer_code, Sales_target3.Product_type_code as Product_type_code, Sales_target3.Product_brand_code as Product_brand_code, Sales_target3.Day_key__sales_target_ as Day_key__sales_target_, Sales_target3.Sales_target as Sales_target from Sales_target3

queryItem.description: Day key for the last day of the month based on month key, used only for join with Sales Staff.
Dagsleutel voor de laatste dag van de maand gebaseerd op maandsleutel, alleen gebruikt voor join met verkooppersoneel.
Dagnyckel för den sista dagen i månaden baserat på månadsnyckel, används bara för sammanfogning med försäljningspersonal.
基于月份键的月份最后一天的天键，仅用于与销售人员配合使用。
基於月份密鑰之月份的最後一天的日密鑰，僅用於與銷售人員相關聯。

基於月份密鑰之月份的最後一天的日密鑰，僅用於與銷售人員相關聯。
Klíč posledního dne měsíce na základě klíče měsíce; používá se jen v kombinaci se zaměstnanci prodeje.
Dagsnøgle for den sidste dag i måneden på basis af månedsnøglen, bruges kun ved møde med salgspersonalet.
Kuukausiavaimeen perustuvan kuun viimeisen päivän päiväavain, jota käytetään vain myyntihenkilökuntaan liittämiseen.
Clé du jour pour le dernier jour du mois basée sur une clé de mois, utilisée seulement pour les jointures avec les métadonnées Personnel de vente.
Tagesschlüssel für den letzten Tag des Monats auf der Grundlage des Monatsschlüssels. Wird nur für die Verbindung mit Vertriebsmitarbeiter verwendet.
Κλειδί ημέρας για την τελευταία ημέρα του μήνα βάσει του κλειδιού μήνα, το οποίο χρησιμοποιείται μόνο για την επικοινωνία με το προσωπικό πωλήσεων.
Havi kulcson alapuló hónapzáró napi kulcs, csak az eladási személyzet egyesítő használatára.
Kata kunci hari untuk hari terakhir dalam bulan berdasarkan kata kunci bulan, hanya gidunakan untuk digabungkan dengan Staf Penjualan.
Chiave giorno per l'ultimo giorno del mese basata sulla chiave mese e utilizzata solo in combinazione con Personale di vendita.
月キーに基づく月の最終日の日キー。営業スタッフとの結合にのみ使用します。
월 키 기준의 월 마지막 날의 날짜 키(영업 직원과 함께 참여할 때만 사용).
Kekunci hari untuk hari terakhir bulan berdasarkan kekunci bulan, yang digunakan untuk gabungan Kakitangan Jualan.
Dagsnøkkel for siste dag i måneden basert på månedsnøkkel, brukes bare for sammenføyning med salgsmedarbeidere.
Klucz dnia dla ostatniego dnia miesiąca bazującego na kluczu miesiąca, stosowany tylko w połączeniu z Działem Sprzedaży.
Ключ даты последнего дня месяца, определенный по ключу месяца и используемый только для объединения с продавцами.
Clave de día del último día del mes basada en la clave de mes, que sólo se utiliza para unirse como personal de ventas.
คีย์วันสำหรับวันสุดท้ายของเดือนตามคีย์เดือน ใช้ร่วมกับพนักงานขายเท่านั้น
基于月份键的月份最后一天的天键，仅用于与销售人员配合使用。
Chave do dia para o último dia do mês com base na chave do mês, usado apenas para associação com Equipe de Vendas.
مفتاح اليوم لآخر يوم من الشهر بناءا على مفتاح الشهر، الذي يستخدم فقط للربط مع فريق المبيعات.
Cheia zilei pentru ultima zi din lună pe baza cheii de lună, utilizată pentru unire cu Personalul de vânzări.
Yalnızca Satış Kadrosuyla birleştirmek için kullanılan ay anahtarına dayalı ayın son günü için gün anahtarı.
Dagsnøkkel for siste dag i måneden basert på månedsnøkkel, brukes bare for sammenføyning med salgsmedarbeidere.
Ključ dana za zadnji dan u mjesecu baziran na ključu mjeseca, koristi se sano za osoblje prodaje.
Ай кілтіне негізделген айдың соңғы күніне арналған күн кілті, Сатылымдар қызметкермен байланыстыру үшін пайдаланылады.
Ključ dneva za zadnji dan v mesecu na osnovi ključa meseca. Uporablja se samo za pridružitev s prodajnim osebjem.

modelQuery.sql: with Sales as (select (((extract(year from ORDER_DETAILS.SHIP_DATE) * 10000) + (extract(month from ORDER_DETAILS.SHIP_DATE) * 100)) + extract(day from ORDER_DETAILS.SHIP_DATE)) as Day_key__ship_date_, (((extract(year from ORDER_HEADER.ORDER_CLOSE_DATE) * 10000) + (extract(month from ORDER_HEADER.ORDER_CLOSE_DATE) * 100)) + extract(day from ORDER_HEADER.ORDER_CLOSE_DATE)) as Day_key__close_date_, (((extract(year from ORDER_HEADER.ORDER_DATE) * 10000) + (extract(month from ORDER_HEADER.ORDER_DATE) * 100)) + extract(day from ORDER_HEADER.ORDER_DATE)) as Day_key__order_date_, ORDER_HEADER.ORDER_NUMBER as Order_number, ORDER_HEADER.RETAILER_NAME as Retailer_name, ORDER_HEADER.RETAILER_NAME_MB as Retailer_name__multiscript_, ORDER_HEADER.RETAILER_SITE_CODE as Retailer_site_code, ORDER_HEADER.RETAILER_CONTACT_CODE as Retailer_contact_code, ORDER_HEADER.SALES_STAFF_CODE as Sales_staff_code, ORDER_HEADER.SALES_BRANCH_CODE as Sales_branch_code, ORDER_HEADER.ORDER_DATE as Order_date, ORDER_HEADER.ORDER_CLOSE_DATE as Order_close_date, ORDER_HEADER.ORDER_METHOD_CODE as Order_method_code, ORDER_DETAILS.ORDER_DETAIL_CODE as Order_detail_code, ORDER_DETAILS.SHIP_DATE as Ship_date, ORDER_DETAILS.PRODUCT_NUMBER as Product_number, ORDER_DETAILS.PROMOTION_CODE as Promotion_code, ORDER_DETAILS.QUANTITY as Quantity, ORDER_DETAILS.UNIT_COST as Unit_cost, ORDER_DETAILS.UNIT_PRICE as Unit_price, ORDER_DETAILS.UNIT_SALE_PRICE as Unit_sale_price, (ORDER_DETAILS.QUANTITY * ORDER_DETAILS.UNIT_SALE_PRICE) as Revenue, (ORDER_DETAILS.QUANTITY * ORDER_DETAILS.UNIT_COST) as Product_cost, ((ORDER_DETAILS.QUANTITY * ORDER_DETAILS.UNIT_SALE_PRICE) - (ORDER_DETAILS.QUANTITY * ORDER_DETAILS.UNIT_COST)) as Gross_profit, (((ORDER_DETAILS.QUANTITY * ORDER_DETAILS.UNIT_SALE_PRICE) - (ORDER_DETAILS.QUANTITY * ORDER_DETAILS.UNIT_COST)) / (ORDER_DETAILS.QUANTITY * ORDER_DETAILS.UNIT_SALE_PRICE)) as Margin, (ORDER_DETAILS.UNIT_PRICE * ORDER_DETAILS.QUANTITY) as Planned_revenue from [gosales].ORDER_DETAILS ORDER_DETAILS, [gosales].ORDER_HEADER ORDER_HEADER where (ORDER_HEADER.ORDER_NUMBER = ORDER_DETAILS.ORDER_NUMBER) ) select Sales.Day_key__ship_date_ as Day_key__ship_date_, Sales.Day_key__close_date_ as Day_key__close_date_, Sales.Day_key__order_date_ as Day_key__order_date_, Sales.Order_number as Order_number, Sales.Retailer_name as Retailer_name, Sales.Retailer_name__multiscript_ as Retailer_name__multiscript_, Sales.Retailer_site_code as Retailer_site_code, Sales.Retailer_contact_code as Retailer_contact_code, Sales.Sales_staff_code as Sales_staff_code, Sales.Sales_branch_code as Sales_branch_code, Sales.Order_date as Order_date, Sales.Order_close_date as Order_close_date, Sales.Order_method_code as Order_method_code, Sales.Order_detail_code as Order_detail_code, Sales.Ship_date as Ship_date, Sales.Product_number as Product_number, Sales.Promotion_code as Promotion_code, Sales.Quantity as Quantity, Sales.Unit_cost as Unit_cost, Sales.Unit_price as Unit_price, Sales.Unit_sale_price as Unit_sale_price, Sales.Revenue as Revenue, Sales.Product_cost as Product_cost, Sales.Gross_profit as Gross_profit, Sales.Margin as Margin, Sales.Planned_revenue as Planned_revenue from Sales

ORDER_DETAILS.ORDER_DETAIL_CODE as Order_detail_code, ORDER_DETAILS.PRODUCT_NUMBER as Product_number from [gosales].ORDER_DETAILS ORDER_DETAILS, [gosales].ORDER_HEADER ORDER_HEADER where (ORDER_HEADER.ORDER_NUMBER = ORDER_DETAILS.ORDER_NUMBER) ), Returned_items as (select (((extract(year from RETURNED_ITEM.RETURN_DATE) * 10000) + (extract(month from RETURNED_ITEM.RETURN_DATE) * 100)) Follow_up_code, RETURNED_ITEM.COMMENTS as Comments, RETURNED_ITEM.DATE_ADVISED as Date_advised from [gosales].RETURNED_ITEM RETURNED_ITEM, Sales where (RETURNED_ITEM.ORDER_DETAIL_CODE = Sales.Order_detail_code) ) select Returned_items.Day_key__return_date_ as Day_key__return_date_, Returned_items.Return_code as Return_code, Returned_items.Return_date as Return_date, Returned_items

modelQuery.sql: with Time__close_date_ as (select TIME_DIMENSION4.CURRENT_YEAR as Year__close_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.QUARTER_KEY as Quarter_key__close_date_, TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP.QUARTER_EN as Quarter__close_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.CURRENT_QUARTER as Quarter__numeric_, TIME_DIMENSION4.MONTH_KEY as Month_key__close_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.MONTH_EN as Month__close_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.CURRENT_MONTH as Month__numeric_, TIME_DIMENSION4.DAYS_IN_MONTH as Days_in_the_month__close_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.DAY_KEY as Day_key__close_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.DAY_DATE as Date__close_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.DAY_OF_WEEK as Day_of_the_week__close_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.DAY_OF_MONTH as Day_of_the_month__close_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.DAY_OF_YEAR as Day_of_the_year__close_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.WEEK_OF_MONTH as Week_of_the_month__close_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.WEEK_OF_QUARTER as c15, TIME_DIMENSION4.WEEK_OF_YEAR as Week_of_the_year__close_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.WEEKDAY_EN as Weekday__close_date_ from [gosales].TIME_DIMENSION TIME_DIMENSION4, [gosales].TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP where (mod(TIME_DIMENSION4.DAY_KEY,100) <> 0) and (TIME_DIMENSION4.QUARTER_KEY = TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP.QUARTER_KEY) ) select Time__close_date_.Year__close_date_ as Year__close_date_, Time__close_date_.Quarter_key__close_date_ as Quarter_key__close_date_, Time__close_date_.Quarter__close_date_ as Quarter__close_date_, Time__close_date_.Quarter__numeric_ as Quarter__numeric_, Time__close_date_.Month_key__close_date_ as Month_key__close_date_, Time__close_date_.Month__close_date_ as Month__close_date_, Time__close_date_.Month__numeric_ as Month__numeric_, Time__close_date_.Days_in_the_month__close_date_ as Days_in_the_month__close_date_, Time__close_date_.Day_key__close_date_ as Day_key__close_date_, Time__close_date_.Date__close_date_ as Date__close_date_, Time__close_date_.Day_of_the_week__close_date_ as Day_of_the_week__close_date_, Time__close_date_.Day_of_the_month__close_date_ as Day_of_the_month__close_date_, Time__close_date_.Day_of_the_year__close_date_ as Day_of_the_year__close_date_, Time__close_date_.Week_of_the_month__close_date_ as Week_of_the_month__close_date_, Time__close_date_.c15 as c15, Time__close_date_.Week_of_the_year__close_date_ as Week_of_the_year__close_date_, Time__close_date_.Weekday__close_date_ as Weekday__close_date_ from Time__close_date_

modelQuery.sql: with PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP6 as (select PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_NUMBER as PRODUCT_NUMBER, PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_NAME as PRODUCT_NAME from [gosales].PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP where (PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_LANGUAGE = N'EN') ), Product_brand7 as (select PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_BRAND_CODE as Product_brand_code, PRODUCT_BRAND.PRODUCT_BRAND_EN as Product_brand_type, PRODUCT_LINE.PRODUCT_LINE_CODE as Product_line_code, PRODUCT_TYPE.PRODUCT_TYPE_CODE as Product_type_code, PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_NUMBER as Product_number, PRODUCT5.BASE_PRODUCT_NUMBER as Base_product_number, PRODUCT5.INTRODUCTION_DATE as Introduction_date, PRODUCT5.DISCONTINUED_DATE as Discontinued_date, PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_COLOR_CODE as Product_color_code, PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_SIZE_CODE as Product_size_code, PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_IMAGE as Product_image, PRODUCT_LINE.PRODUCT_LINE_EN as Product_line, PRODUCT_TYPE.PRODUCT_TYPE_EN as Product_type, PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP6.PRODUCT_NAME as Product_name, PRODUCT_SIZE_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_SIZE_EN as Product_size, PRODUCT_COLOR_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_COLOR_EN as Product_color from [gosales].PRODUCT PRODUCT5, [gosales].PRODUCT_BRAND PRODUCT_BRAND, [gosales].PRODUCT_LINE PRODUCT_LINE, [gosales].PRODUCT_TYPE PRODUCT_TYPE, PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP6, [gosales].PRODUCT_SIZE_LOOKUP PRODUCT_SIZE_LOOKUP, [gosales].PRODUCT_COLOR_LOOKUP PRODUCT_COLOR_LOOKUP where (PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_NUMBER = PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP6.PRODUCT_NUMBER) and (PRODUCT_COLOR_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_COLOR_CODE = PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_COLOR_CODE) and (PRODUCT_SIZE_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_SIZE_CODE = PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_SIZE_CODE) and (PRODUCT_BRAND.PRODUCT_BRAND_CODE = PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_BRAND_CODE) and (PRODUCT_TYPE.PRODUCT_TYPE_CODE = PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_TYPE_CODE) and (PRODUCT_LINE.PRODUCT_LINE_CODE = PRODUCT_TYPE.PRODUCT_LINE_CODE) ) select Product_brand7.Product_brand_code as Product_brand_code, Product_brand7.Product_brand_type as Product_brand_type, Product_brand7.Product_line_code as Product_line_code, Product_brand7.Product_type_code as Product_type_code, Product_brand7.Product_number as Product_number, Product_brand7.Base_product_number as Base_product_number, Product_brand7.Introduction_date as Introduction_date, Product_brand7.Discontinued_date as Discontinued_date, Product_brand7.Product_color_code as Product_color_code, Product_brand7.Product_size_code as Product_size_code, Product_brand7.Product_image as Product_image, Product_brand7.Product_line as Product_line, Product_brand7.Product_type as Product_type, Product_brand7.Product_name as Product_name, Product_brand7.Product_size as Product_size, Product_brand7.Product_color as Product_color from Product_brand7

modelQuery.sql: with Retailer_site5 as (select SALES_REGION.SALES_REGION_CODE as Sales_region_code, SALES_REGION.SALES_REGION_EN as Sales_region, RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_COUNTRY_CODE as Retailer_country_code, COUNTRY.COUNTRY_EN as Retailer_country, RETAILER_SITE4.RETAILER_CODE as Retailer_code, RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_ADDRESS1 as Retailer_address_1, RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_ADDRESS2 as Retailer_address_2, RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_CITY as Retailer_city, RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_PROV_STATE as Retailer_Province_State, RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_POSTAL_ZONE as Retailer_postal_zone, RETAILER_SITE4.RETAILER_SITE_START_DATE as Retailer_site_start_date, RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_ACTIVITY_STATUS_CODE as Retailer_activity_status_code, RETAILER.COMPANY_NAME as Retailer_name, RETAILER.COMPANY_NAME_MB as Retailer_name__multiscript_, RETAILER_SITE4.RETAILER_SITE_CODE as Retailer_site_code, RETAILER_SITE_MB.RTL_ADDRESS1 as c16, RETAILER_SITE_MB.RTL_ADDRESS2 as c17, RETAILER_SITE_MB.RTL_CITY as Retailer_city__multiscript_, RETAILER_SITE_MB.RTL_PROV_STATE as c19, RETAILER_SITE_MB.RTL_POSTAL_ZONE as c20, RETAILER_CONTACT.RETAILER_CONTACT_CODE as Retailer_contact_code, RETAILER_CONTACT.FIRST_NAME as Contact_first_name, RETAILER_CONTACT.LAST_NAME as Contact_last_name, RETAILER_CONTACT.FIRST_NAME_MB as c24, RETAILER_CONTACT.LAST_NAME_MB as c25, ((RETAILER_CONTACT.FIRST_NAME || N' ') || RETAILER_CONTACT.LAST_NAME) as Contact_name, RETAILER_CONTACT.GENDER_CODE as Gender_code, GENDER_LOOKUP.GENDER_EN as Gender, RETAILER_CONTACT.JOB_POSITION_EN as Retailer_contact_position, RETAILER_CONTACT.PHONE_NUMBER as Phone_number, RETAILER_CONTACT.EXTENSION as Extension, RETAILER_CONTACT.FAX as Fax, RETAILER_CONTACT.EMAIL as Email, RETAILER.COMPANY_NAME as Company_name from [gosales].SALES_REGION SALES_REGION, [gosales1].RETAILER_SITE RETAILER_SITE4, [gosales].COUNTRY COUNTRY, [gosales1].RETAILER RETAILER, [gosales1].RETAILER_SITE_MB RETAILER_SITE_MB, [gosales1].RETAILER_CONTACT RETAILER_CONTACT, [gosales2].GENDER_LOOKUP GENDER_LOOKUP where (COUNTRY.SALES_REGION_CODE = SALES_REGION.SALES_REGION_CODE) and (RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_COUNTRY_CODE = COUNTRY.COUNTRY_CODE) and (RETAILER_SITE4.RETAILER_SITE_CODE = RETAILER_CONTACT.RETAILER_SITE_CODE) and (RETAILER_CONTACT.RETAILER_SITE_CODE = RETAILER_SITE_MB.RETAILER_SITE_CODE) and (RETAILER_CONTACT.GENDER_CODE = GENDER_LOOKUP.GENDER_CODE) and (RETAILER_SITE4.RETAILER_CODE = RETAILER.RETAILER_CODE) ) select Retailer_site5.Sales_region_code as Sales_region_code, Retailer_site5.Sales_region as Sales_region, Retailer_site5.Retailer_country_code as Retailer_country_code, Retailer_site5.Retailer_country as Retailer_country, Retailer_site5.Retailer_code as Retailer_code, Retailer_site5.Retailer_address_1 as Retailer_address_1, Retailer_site5.Retailer_address_2 as Retailer_address_2, Retailer_site5.Retailer_city as Retailer_city, Retailer_site5.Retailer_Province_State as Retailer_Province_State, Retailer_site5.Retailer_postal_zone as Retailer_postal_zone, Retailer_site5.Retailer_site_start_date as Retailer_site_start_date, Retailer_site5.Retailer_activity_status_code as Retailer_activity_status_code, Retailer_site5.Retailer_name as Retailer_name, Retailer_site5.Retailer_name__multiscript_ as Retailer_name__multiscript_, Retailer_site5.Retailer_site_code as Retailer_site_code, Retailer_site5.c16 as c16, Retailer_site5.c17 as c17, Retailer_site5.Retailer_city__multiscript_ as Retailer_city__multiscript_, Retailer_site5.c19 as c19, Retailer_site5.c20 as c20, Retailer_site5.Retailer_contact_code as Retailer_contact_code, Retailer_site5.Contact_first_name as Contact_first_name, Retailer_site5.Contact_last_name as Contact_last_name, Retailer_site5.c24 as c24, Retailer_site5.c25 as c25, Retailer_site5.Contact_name as Contact_name, Retailer_site5.Gender_code as Gender_code, Retailer_site5.Gender as Gender, Retailer_site5.Retailer_contact_position as Retailer_contact_position, Retailer_site5.Phone_number as Phone_number, Retailer_site5.Extension as Extension, Retailer_site5.Fax as Fax, Retailer_site5.Email as Email, Retailer_site5.Company_name as Company_name from Retailer_site5

modelQuery.sql: with Manager as (select EMPLOYEE.EMPLOYEE_CODE as Manager_code, EMPLOYEE.WORK_PHONE as Manager_phone, EMPLOYEE.EXTENSION as Manager_extension, EMPLOYEE.FAX as Manager_fax, EMPLOYEE.EMAIL as Manager_email from [gosales2].EMPLOYEE EMPLOYEE, [gosales2].EMPLOYEE_HISTORY EMPLOYEE_HISTORY where (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.RECORD_END_DATE is NULL) and (EMPLOYEE.EMPLOYEE_CODE = EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.EMPLOYEE_CODE) ), Sales_staff as (select COUNTRY.SALES_REGION_CODE as Sales_region_code, SALES_REGION.SALES_REGION_EN as Sales_region, BRANCH.COUNTRY_CODE as Country_code, COUNTRY.COUNTRY_EN as Country, BRANCH.CITY as City, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.BRANCH_CODE as Branch_code, EMPLOYEE.EMPLOYEE_CODE as Sales_staff_code, EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME as First_name, EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME_MB as First_name__multiscript_, EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME as Last_name, EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME_MB as Last_name__multiscript_, EMPLOYEE.DATE_HIRED as Date_hired, EMPLOYEE.TERMINATION_DATE as Termination_date, EMPLOYEE.TERMINATION_CODE as Termination_code, EMPLOYEE.BIRTH_DATE as Birth_date, EMPLOYEE.GENDER_CODE as Gender_code, EMPLOYEE.WORK_PHONE as Work_phone, EMPLOYEE.EXTENSION as Extension, EMPLOYEE.FAX as Fax, EMPLOYEE.EMAIL as Email, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.EMPLOYEE_HISTORY_PARENT as Employee_history_parent, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.EMPLOYEE_HISTORY_CODE as Employee_history_code, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.RECORD_START_DATE as Record_start_date, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.RECORD_END_DATE as Record_end_date, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.POSITION_CODE as Position_code, POSITION_LOOKUP.POSITION_EN as Position26, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.POSITION_START_DATE as Position_start_date, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.MANAGER_CODE as Manager_code, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.MANAGER as Manager, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.MANAGER_MB as Manager__multiscript_, Manager.Manager_phone as Manager_phone, Manager.Manager_extension as Manager_extension, Manager.Manager_fax as Manager_fax, Manager.Manager_email as Manager_email, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.ORGANIZATION_CODE as Organization_code, ORGANIZATION.ORGANIZATION_NAME_EN as Organization, BRANCH.ADDRESS1 as Address_1, BRANCH.ADDRESS1_MB as Address_1__multiscript_, BRANCH.ADDRESS2 as Address_2, BRANCH.ADDRESS2_MB as Address_2__multiscript_, BRANCH.CITY_MB as City__multiscript_, BRANCH.PROV_STATE as Province_State, BRANCH.PROV_STATE_MB as Province_State__multiscript_, BRANCH.POSTAL_ZONE as Postal_zone, POSITION_DEPARTMENT.DEPARTMENT_CODE as Department_code, POSITION_DEPARTMENT.DEPARTMENT_PARENT as Department_parent, GENDER_LOOKUP.GENDER_EN as Gender, ((EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME || N' ') || EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME) as Staff_name, case when (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.BRANCH_CODE in (25,26)) then (((EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME_MB || N' ') || EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME_MB) || cast('様' as nchar (1))) when (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.BRANCH_CODE in (32,33,34)) then ((EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME_MB || N' ') || EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME_MB) else ((EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME_MB || N' ') || EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME_MB) end as Staff_name__multiscript_ from [gosales].COUNTRY COUNTRY, [gosales].SALES_REGION SALES_REGION, [gosales].BRANCH BRANCH, [gosales2].EMPLOYEE_HISTORY EMPLOYEE_HISTORY, [gosales2].EMPLOYEE EMPLOYEE, [gosales2].POSITION_LOOKUP POSITION_LOOKUP, Manager, [gosales2].ORGANIZATION ORGANIZATION, [gosales2].POSITION_DEPARTMENT POSITION_DEPARTMENT, [gosales2].GENDER_LOOKUP GENDER_LOOKUP where (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.RECORD_END_DATE is NULL) and (COUNTRY.COUNTRY_CODE = BRANCH.COUNTRY_CODE) and (ORGANIZATION.ORGANIZATION_CODE = BRANCH.ORGANIZATION_CODE) and (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.ORGANIZATION_CODE = ORGANIZATION.ORGANIZATION_CODE) and (EMPLOYEE.EMPLOYEE_CODE = EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.EMPLOYEE_CODE) and (GENDER_LOOKUP.GENDER_CODE = EMPLOYEE.GENDER_CODE) and (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.POSITION_CODE = POSITION_DEPARTMENT.POSITION_CODE) and (POSITION_DEPARTMENT.POSITION_CODE = POSITION_LOOKUP.POSITION_CODE) and (Manager.Manager_code = EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.MANAGER_CODE) and (COUNTRY.SALES_REGION_CODE = SALES_REGION.SALES_REGION_CODE) ) select Sales_staff.Sales_region_code as Sales_region_code, Sales_staff.Sales_region as Sales_region, Sales_staff.Country_code as Country_code, Sales_staff.Country as Country, Sales_staff.City as City, Sales_staff.Branch_code as Branch_code, Sales_staff.Sales_staff_code as Sales_staff_code, Sales_staff.First_name as First_name, Sales_staff.First_name__multiscript_ as First_name__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Last_name as Last_name, Sales_staff.Last_name__multiscript_ as Last_name__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Date_hired as Date_hired, Sales_staff.Termination_date as Termination_date, Sales_staff.Termination_code as Termination_code, Sales_staff.Birth_date as Birth_date, Sales_staff.Gender_code as Gender_code, Sales_staff.Work_phone as Work_phone, Sales_staff.Extension as Extension, Sales_staff.Fax as Fax, Sales_staff.Email as Email, Sales_staff.Employee_history_parent as Employee_history_parent, Sales_staff.Employee_history_code as Employee_history_code, Sales_staff.Record_start_date as Record_start_date, Sales_staff.Record_end_date as Record_end_date, Sales_staff.Position_code as Position_code, Sales_staff.Position26 as Position26, Sales_staff.Position_start_date as Position_start_date, Sales_staff.Manager_code as Manager_code, Sales_staff.Manager as Manager, Sales_staff.Manager__multiscript_ as Manager__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Manager_phone as Manager_phone, Sales_staff.Manager_extension as Manager_extension, Sales_staff.Manager_fax as Manager_fax, Sales_staff.Manager_email as Manager_email, Sales_staff.Organization_code as Organization_code, Sales_staff.Organization as Organization, Sales_staff.Address_1 as Address_1, Sales_staff.Address_1__multiscript_ as Address_1__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Address_2 as Address_2, Sales_staff.Address_2__multiscript_ as Address_2__multiscript_, Sales_staff.City__multiscript_ as City__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Province_State as Province_State, Sales_staff.Province_State__multiscript_ as Province_State__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Postal_zone as Postal_zone, Sales_staff.Department_code as Department_code, Sales_staff.Department_parent as Department_parent, Sales_staff.Gender as Gender, Sales_staff.Staff_name as Staff_name, Sales_staff.Staff_name__multiscript_ as Staff_name__multiscript_ from Sales_staff

modelQuery.sql: with Manager as (select EMPLOYEE.EMPLOYEE_CODE as Manager_code, ((EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME || N' ') || EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME) as Manager_name, case when (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.BRANCH_CODE in (25,26)) then (((EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME_MB || N' ') || EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME_MB) || cast('様' as nchar (1))) when (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.BRANCH_CODE in (32,33,34)) then ((EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME_MB || N' ') || EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME_MB) else ((EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME_MB || N' ') || EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME_MB) end as Manager_name__multiscript_, EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME as Manager_first_name, EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME_MB as c5, EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME as Manager_last_name, EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME_MB as c7, EMPLOYEE.WORK_PHONE as Manager_phone, EMPLOYEE.EXTENSION as Manager_extension, EMPLOYEE.FAX as Manager_fax, EMPLOYEE.EMAIL as Manager_email from [gosales2].EMPLOYEE EMPLOYEE, [gosales2].EMPLOYEE_HISTORY EMPLOYEE_HISTORY where (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.RECORD_END_DATE is NULL) and (EMPLOYEE.EMPLOYEE_CODE = EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.EMPLOYEE_CODE) ) select Manager.Manager_code as Manager_code, Manager.Manager_name as Manager_name, Manager.Manager_name__multiscript_ as Manager_name__multiscript_, Manager.Manager_first_name as Manager_first_name, Manager.c5 as c5, Manager.Manager_last_name as Manager_last_name, Manager.c7 as c7, Manager.Manager_phone as Manager_phone, Manager.Manager_extension as Manager_extension, Manager.Manager_fax as Manager_fax, Manager.Manager_email as Manager_email from Manager

modelQuery.sql: with PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP6 as (select PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_NUMBER as PRODUCT_NUMBER, PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_NAME as PRODUCT_NAME, PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION as PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION from [gosales].PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP where (PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_LANGUAGE = N'EN') ), Products as (select PRODUCT_LINE.PRODUCT_LINE_CODE as Product_line_code, PRODUCT_LINE.PRODUCT_LINE_EN as Product_line, PRODUCT_TYPE.PRODUCT_TYPE_CODE as Product_type_code, PRODUCT_TYPE.PRODUCT_TYPE_EN as Product_type, PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_NUMBER as Product_number, PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP6.PRODUCT_NAME as Product, PRODUCT5.BASE_PRODUCT_NUMBER as Base_product_number, PRODUCT5.INTRODUCTION_DATE as Introduction_date, PRODUCT5.DISCONTINUED_DATE as Discontinued_date, PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_COLOR_CODE as Product_color_code, PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_SIZE_CODE as Product_size_code, PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_BRAND_CODE as Product_brand_code, (N'../samples/images/' || PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_IMAGE) as Product_image, PRODUCT_SIZE_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_SIZE_EN as Product_size, PRODUCT_BRAND.PRODUCT_BRAND_EN as Product_brand, PRODUCT_COLOR_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_COLOR_EN as Product_color, PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP6.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION as Product_description from [gosales].PRODUCT_LINE PRODUCT_LINE, [gosales].PRODUCT_TYPE PRODUCT_TYPE, [gosales].PRODUCT PRODUCT5, PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP6, [gosales].PRODUCT_SIZE_LOOKUP PRODUCT_SIZE_LOOKUP, [gosales].PRODUCT_BRAND PRODUCT_BRAND, [gosales].PRODUCT_COLOR_LOOKUP PRODUCT_COLOR_LOOKUP where (PRODUCT_LINE.PRODUCT_LINE_CODE = PRODUCT_TYPE.PRODUCT_LINE_CODE) and (PRODUCT_TYPE.PRODUCT_TYPE_CODE = PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_TYPE_CODE) and (PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_NUMBER = PRODUCT_NAME_LOOKUP6.PRODUCT_NUMBER) and (PRODUCT_COLOR_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_COLOR_CODE = PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_COLOR_CODE) and (PRODUCT_SIZE_LOOKUP.PRODUCT_SIZE_CODE = PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_SIZE_CODE) and (PRODUCT_BRAND.PRODUCT_BRAND_CODE = PRODUCT5.PRODUCT_BRAND_CODE) ) select Products.Product_line_code as Product_line_code, Products.Product_line as Product_line, Products.Product_type_code as Product_type_code, Products.Product_type as Product_type, Products.Base_product_number as Base_product_number, Products.Product as Product, Products.Product_number as Product_number, Products.Introduction_date as Introduction_date, Products.Product_size_code as Product_size_code, Products.Product_image as Product_image, Products.Product_description as Product_description, Products.Product_brand as Product_brand, Products.Product_brand_code as Product_brand_code, Products.Product_size as Product_size, Products.Discontinued_date as Discontinued_date, Products.Product_color as Product_color, Products.Product_color_code as Product_color_code, ((Products.Product || N' ') || cast(Products.Product_number as varchar (6))) as Product_details from Products

COUNTRY.COUNTRY_EN as Retailer_country, RETAILER_SITE4.RETAILER_CODE as Retailer_code, RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_ADDRESS1 as Retailer_address_1, RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_ADDRESS2 as Retailer_address_2, RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_CITY as Retailer_site, RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_PROV_STATE as Retailer_Province_State, RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_POSTAL_ZONE as Retailer_postal_zone, RETAILER_SITE4.RETAILER_SITE_START_DATE as Retailer_site_start_date, RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_ACTIVITY_STATUS_CODE as Retailer_activity_status_code, RETAILER.COMPANY_NAME as Retailer, RETAILER.COMPANY_NAME_MB as Retailer__multiscript_, RETAILER_SITE4.RETAILER_SITE_CODE as Retailer_site_code, RETAILER_SITE_MB.RTL_ADDRESS1 as c17, RETAILER_SITE_MB.RTL_ADDRESS2 as c18, RETAILER_SITE_MB.RTL_CITY as Retailer_city__multiscript_, RETAILER_SITE_MB.RTL_PROV_STATE as c20, RETAILER_SITE_MB.RTL_POSTAL_ZONE as c21, RETAILER_CONTACT.RETAILER_CONTACT_CODE as Retailer_contact_code, RETAILER_CONTACT.FIRST_NAME as Contact_first_name, RETAILER_CONTACT.LAST_NAME as Contact_last_name, RETAILER_CONTACT.FIRST_NAME_MB as c25, RETAILER_CONTACT.LAST_NAME_MB as c26, ((RETAILER_CONTACT.FIRST_NAME || N' ') || RETAILER_CONTACT.LAST_NAME) as Contact_name, RETAILER_CONTACT.GENDER_CODE as Gender_code, GENDER_LOOKUP.GENDER_EN as Gender, RETAILER_CONTACT.JOB_POSITION_EN as Retailer_contact_position, RETAILER_CONTACT.PHONE_NUMBER as Phone_number, RETAILER_CONTACT.EXTENSION as Extension, RETAILER_CONTACT.FAX as Fax, RETAILER_CONTACT.EMAIL as Email from [gosales].SALES_REGION SALES_REGION, [gosales1].RETAILER_SITE RETAILER_SITE4, [gosales].COUNTRY COUNTRY, [gosales1].RETAILER RETAILER, [gosales1].RETAILER_SITE_MB RETAILER_SITE_MB, [gosales1].RETAILER_CONTACT RETAILER_CONTACT, [gosales2].GENDER_LOOKUP GENDER_LOOKUP where (COUNTRY.SALES_REGION_CODE = SALES_REGION.SALES_REGION_CODE) and (RETAILER_SITE4.RTL_COUNTRY_CODE = COUNTRY.COUNTRY_CODE) and (RETAILER_SITE4.RETAILER_SITE_CODE = RETAILER_CONTACT.RETAILER_SITE_CODE) and (RETAILER_CONTACT.GENDER_CODE = GENDER_LOOKUP.GENDER_CODE) and (RETAILER_CONTACT.RETAILER_SITE_CODE = RETAILER_SITE_MB.RETAILER_SITE_CODE) and (RETAILER_SITE4.RETAILER_CODE = RETAILER.RETAILER_CODE) ) select Retailers.Sales_region_code as Sales_region_code, Retailers.Region as Sales_region, Retailers.Retailer_country_code as Retailer_country_code, Retailers.Retailer_country as Retailer_country, Retailers.Retailer_code as Retailer_code, Retailers.Retailer as Retailer_name, Retailers.Retailer__multiscript_ as Retailer_name__multiscript_, Retailers.Retailer_address_1 as Retailer_address_1, Retailers.Retailer_address_2 as Retailer_address_2, Retailers.Retailer_site as Retailer_city, Retailers.Retailer_Province_State as Retailer_Province_State, Retailers.Retailer_postal_zone as Retailer_postal_zone, Retailers.Retailer_site_start_date as Retailer_site_start_date, Retailers.Retailer_activity_status_code as Retailer_activity_status_code, Retailers.Retailer_site_code as Retailer_site_code, Retailers.c17 as c16, Retailers.c18 as c17, Retailers.Retailer_city__multiscript_ as Retailer_city__multiscript_, Retailers.c20 as c19, Retailers.c21 as c20, Retailers.Retailer_contact_code as Retailer_contact_code, Retailers.Contact_first_name as Contact_first_name, Retailers.Contact_last_name as Contact_last_name, Retailers.c25 as c24, Retailers.c26 as c25, Retailers.Contact_name as Contact_name, Retailers.Phone_number as Phone_number, Retailers.Extension as Extension, Retailers.Fax as Fax, Retailers.Email as Email, Retailers.Gender_code as Gender_code, Retailers.Gender as Gender, Retailers.Retailer_contact_position as Retailer_contact_position from Retailers

modelQuery.sql: with Manager as (select EMPLOYEE.EMPLOYEE_CODE as Manager_code, EMPLOYEE.WORK_PHONE as Manager_phone, EMPLOYEE.EXTENSION as Manager_extension, EMPLOYEE.FAX as Manager_fax, EMPLOYEE.EMAIL as Manager_email from [gosales2].EMPLOYEE EMPLOYEE, [gosales2].EMPLOYEE_HISTORY EMPLOYEE_HISTORY where (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.RECORD_END_DATE is NULL) and (EMPLOYEE.EMPLOYEE_CODE = EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.EMPLOYEE_CODE) ), Sales_staff as (select COUNTRY.SALES_REGION_CODE as Sales_region_code, SALES_REGION.SALES_REGION_EN as Sales_region, BRANCH.COUNTRY_CODE as Country_code, COUNTRY.COUNTRY_EN as Country, BRANCH.CITY as City, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.BRANCH_CODE as Branch_code, EMPLOYEE.EMPLOYEE_CODE as Sales_staff_code, EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME as First_name, EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME_MB as First_name__multiscript_, EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME as Last_name, EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME_MB as Last_name__multiscript_, EMPLOYEE.DATE_HIRED as Date_hired, EMPLOYEE.TERMINATION_DATE as Termination_date, EMPLOYEE.TERMINATION_CODE as Termination_code, EMPLOYEE.BIRTH_DATE as Birth_date, EMPLOYEE.GENDER_CODE as Gender_code, EMPLOYEE.WORK_PHONE as Work_phone, EMPLOYEE.EXTENSION as Extension, EMPLOYEE.FAX as Fax, EMPLOYEE.EMAIL as Email, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.EMPLOYEE_HISTORY_PARENT as Employee_history_parent, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.EMPLOYEE_HISTORY_CODE as Employee_history_code, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.RECORD_START_DATE as Record_start_date, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.RECORD_END_DATE as Record_end_date, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.POSITION_CODE as Position_code, POSITION_LOOKUP.POSITION_EN as Position26, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.POSITION_START_DATE as Position_start_date, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.MANAGER_CODE as Manager_code, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.MANAGER as Manager, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.MANAGER_MB as Manager__multiscript_, EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.ORGANIZATION_CODE as Organization_code, ORGANIZATION.ORGANIZATION_NAME_EN as Organization, BRANCH.ADDRESS1 as Address_1, BRANCH.ADDRESS1_MB as Address_1__multiscript_, BRANCH.ADDRESS2 as Address_2, BRANCH.ADDRESS2_MB as Address_2__multiscript_, BRANCH.CITY_MB as City__multiscript_, BRANCH.PROV_STATE as Province_State, BRANCH.PROV_STATE_MB as Province_State__multiscript_, BRANCH.POSTAL_ZONE as Postal_zone, POSITION_DEPARTMENT.DEPARTMENT_CODE as Department_code, POSITION_DEPARTMENT.DEPARTMENT_PARENT as Department_parent, GENDER_LOOKUP.GENDER_EN as Gender, ((EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME || N' ') || EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME) as Staff_name, case when (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.BRANCH_CODE in (25,26)) then (((EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME_MB || N' ') || EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME_MB) || cast('様' as nchar (1))) when (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.BRANCH_CODE in (32,33,34)) then ((EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME_MB || N' ') || EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME_MB) else ((EMPLOYEE.FIRST_NAME_MB || N' ') || EMPLOYEE.LAST_NAME_MB) end as Staff_name__multiscript_ from [gosales].COUNTRY COUNTRY, [gosales].SALES_REGION SALES_REGION, [gosales].BRANCH BRANCH, [gosales2].EMPLOYEE_HISTORY EMPLOYEE_HISTORY, [gosales2].EMPLOYEE EMPLOYEE, [gosales2].POSITION_LOOKUP POSITION_LOOKUP, Manager, [gosales2].ORGANIZATION ORGANIZATION, [gosales2].POSITION_DEPARTMENT POSITION_DEPARTMENT, [gosales2].GENDER_LOOKUP GENDER_LOOKUP where (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.RECORD_END_DATE is NULL) and (COUNTRY.COUNTRY_CODE = BRANCH.COUNTRY_CODE) and (ORGANIZATION.ORGANIZATION_CODE = BRANCH.ORGANIZATION_CODE) and (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.ORGANIZATION_CODE = ORGANIZATION.ORGANIZATION_CODE) and (EMPLOYEE.EMPLOYEE_CODE = EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.EMPLOYEE_CODE) and (GENDER_LOOKUP.GENDER_CODE = EMPLOYEE.GENDER_CODE) and (EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.POSITION_CODE = POSITION_DEPARTMENT.POSITION_CODE) and (POSITION_DEPARTMENT.POSITION_CODE = POSITION_LOOKUP.POSITION_CODE) and (Manager.Manager_code = EMPLOYEE_HISTORY.MANAGER_CODE) and (COUNTRY.SALES_REGION_CODE = SALES_REGION.SALES_REGION_CODE) ) select Sales_staff.Sales_region_code as Sales_region_code, Sales_staff.Sales_region as Sales_region, Sales_staff.Country_code as Country_code, Sales_staff.Country as Country, Sales_staff.City as City, Sales_staff.Branch_code as Branch_code, Sales_staff.City__multiscript_ as City__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Sales_staff_code as Sales_staff_code, Sales_staff.First_name as First_name, Sales_staff.First_name__multiscript_ as First_name__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Department_parent as Department_parent, Sales_staff.Last_name as Last_name, Sales_staff.Last_name__multiscript_ as Last_name__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Staff_name as Staff_name, Sales_staff.Staff_name__multiscript_ as Staff_name__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Date_hired as Date_hired, Sales_staff.Termination_date as Termination_date, Sales_staff.Termination_code as Termination_code, Sales_staff.Birth_date as Birth_date, Sales_staff.Gender_code as Gender_code, Sales_staff.Work_phone as Work_phone, Sales_staff.Extension as Extension, Sales_staff.Fax as Fax, Sales_staff.Email as Email, Sales_staff.Employee_history_parent as Employee_history_parent, Sales_staff.Employee_history_code as Employee_history_code, Sales_staff.Record_start_date as Record_start_date, Sales_staff.Record_end_date as Record_end_date, Sales_staff.Position_code as Position_code, Sales_staff.Position26 as Position30, Sales_staff.Position_start_date as Position_start_date, Sales_staff.Manager_code as Manager_code, Sales_staff.Manager as Manager, Sales_staff.Manager__multiscript_ as Manager__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Organization_code as Organization_code, Sales_staff.Organization as Organization, Sales_staff.Address_1 as Address_1, Sales_staff.Address_1__multiscript_ as Address_1__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Address_2 as Address_2, Sales_staff.Address_2__multiscript_ as Address_2__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Province_State as Province_State, Sales_staff.Province_State__multiscript_ as Province_State__multiscript_, Sales_staff.Postal_zone as Postal_zone, Sales_staff.Department_code as Department_code, Sales_staff.Gender as Gender from Sales_staff

modelQuery.sql: select cast(TIME_DIMENSION3.CURRENT_YEAR as character (4)) as Year1, TIME_DIMENSION3.QUARTER_KEY as Quarter_key, TIME_DIMENSION3.CURRENT_QUARTER as Quarter__numeric_, TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP.QUARTER_EN as Quarter, ((TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP.QUARTER_EN || N' ') || cast(TIME_DIMENSION3.CURRENT_YEAR as varchar (4))) as Quarter__caption_, TIME_DIMENSION3.MONTH_KEY as Month_key, TIME_DIMENSION3.CURRENT_MONTH as Month__numeric_, TIME_DIMENSION3.DAYS_IN_MONTH as Days_in_the_month, ((TIME_DIMENSION3.MONTH_EN || N' ') || cast(TIME_DIMENSION3.CURRENT_YEAR as varchar (4))) as Month__caption_, TIME_DIMENSION3.MONTH_EN as Month10, cast(TIME_DIMENSION3.DAY_KEY as character (8)) as Day_key, TIME_DIMENSION3.DAY_DATE as Date12, TIME_DIMENSION3.DAY_OF_WEEK as Day_of_the_week, TIME_DIMENSION3.DAY_OF_MONTH as Day_of_the_month, TIME_DIMENSION3.DAY_OF_YEAR as Day_of_the_year, TIME_DIMENSION3.WEEK_OF_MONTH as Week_of_the_month, TIME_DIMENSION3.WEEK_OF_QUARTER as Week_of_the_quarter, TIME_DIMENSION3.WEEK_OF_YEAR as Week_of_the_year, TIME_DIMENSION3.WEEKDAY_EN as Weekday from [gosales].TIME_DIMENSION TIME_DIMENSION3, [gosales].TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP where (mod(TIME_DIMENSION3.MONTH_KEY,100) <> 0) and (TIME_DIMENSION3.QUARTER_KEY = TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP.QUARTER_KEY) order by Year1 asc, Quarter_key asc, Month_key asc, Day_key asc

TIME_DIMENSION4.WEEKDAY_EN as Weekday__close_date_ from [gosales].TIME_DIMENSION TIME_DIMENSION4, [gosales].TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP where (mod(TIME_DIMENSION4.DAY_KEY,100) <> 0) and Quarter__ship_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.CURRENT_QUARTER as Quarter__numeric_, TIME_DIMENSION4.MONTH_KEY as Month_key__ship_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.MONTH_EN as Month__ship_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.CURRENT_MONTH as Month__numeric_, TIME_DIMENSION4.DAY_KEY as Day_key__ship_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.DAY_DATE as Date__ship_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.DAY_OF_WEEK as Day_of_the_week__ship_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.DAY_OF_MONTH as Day_of_the_month__ship_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.DAYS_IN_MONTH as Days_in_the_month__ship_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.DAY_OF_YEAR as Day_of_the_year__ship_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.WEEK_OF_MONTH as Week_of_the_month__ship_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.WEEK_OF_QUARTER as c15, TIME_DIMENSION4.WEEK_OF_YEAR as Week_of_the_year__ship_date_, TIME_DIMENSION4.WEEKDAY_EN as Weekday__ship_date_ from [gosales].TIME_DIMENSION TIME_DIMENSION4, [gosales].TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP where (mod(TIME_DIMENSION4.DAY_KEY,100) <> 0) and (TIME_DIMENSION4.QUARTER_KEY = TIME_QUARTER_LOOKUP.QUARTER_KEY) ) select cast(Time__ship_date_.Year__ship_date_ as character (4)) as Current_year__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.Quarter_key__ship_date_ as Quarter_key__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.Quarter__numeric_ as Current_quarter__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.Quarter__ship_date_ as Quarter__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.Month_key__ship_date_ as Month_key__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.Month__ship_date_ as Month__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.Days_in_the_month__ship_date_ as Days_in_the_month__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.Month__numeric_ as Current_month__ship_date_, cast(Time__ship_date_.Day_key__ship_date_ as character (8)) as Day_key__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.Date__ship_date_ as Date__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.Day_of_the_week__ship_date_ as Day_of_the_week__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.Day_of_the_month__ship_date_ as Day_of_the_month__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.Day_of_the_year__ship_date_ as Day_of_the_year__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.Week_of_the_month__ship_date_ as Week_of_the_month__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.c15 as c15, Time__ship_date_.Week_of_the_year__ship_date_ as Week_of_the_year__ship_date_, Time__ship_date_.Weekday__ship_date_ as Weekday__ship_date_ from Time__ship_date_
